; Stage entity setup (ocarina backdrop + assistant spawn stubs)
; ============================================================
; Each assistant is spawned via one of three executor families:
;   - slot 2 stubs at .executor_2_1465E8..1467E0 (assistant 1)
;   - slot 3 stubs at .executor_3_146818..146A10 (assistant 2)
;   - slot 4 stubs at .executor_4_146A24..146BD4 (assistant 3)
; Stubs differ only in the SETUP_ENTITY asset id and spawn coords,
; then drop into the shared wait loop.
; ============================================================

